title: #64: Diabeetus (Rick Ingraham)
itunes:title: Diabeetus with Rick Ingraham
description: Rick Ingraham and I went into the old Comedy Store phone room to talk about his medical problems. Ingraham's stomach has been a cauldren of hatred for the last half decade or so and recently found out that he's got childhood dieabetes. Listen to the story of this crazy medical problem by a hilarious comedian.
